Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/Minh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-gia-hu%E1%BA%A5n/poem-3aa2tlihTrwlAHWnLopSow">Minh Đạo gia huấn - 明道家訓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/author-f6hExEIODG8dBbnhIj50jQ">Trình Hạo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1c/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-s%E1%BB%A9-%C4%91%C4%83ng-tr%C3%ACnh-t%E1%BB%B1-thu%E1%BA%ADt/poem-Jbo4CE9Vim98vO5_8l--SA">Phụng sứ đăng trình tự thuật - 奉使登程自述</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-KlUCS3ER6VvH2W9Ma4g25A">Nguyễn Thực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/T%E1%BA%B7ng-L%E1%BA%A1ng-Giang-gi%C3%A1o-th%E1%BB%A5-L%C3%AA-chi-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Kh%C3%AA-tri-huy%E1%BB%87n/poem-wgBh9QYrFsscBrAfgqhCHg">Tặng Lạng Giang giáo thụ Lê chi Hương Khê tri huyện - 贈涼江教授黎之香溪知縣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Ph%E1%BB%A5c/Th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn-T%C3%A2y-H%E1%BB%93-tr%C3%BAc-chi-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-taSPujsqQZuLeRR63h1WVw">Thứ vận Tây Hồ trúc chi ca kỳ 4 - 次韻西湖竹枝歌其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Ph%E1%BB%A5c/author-uaU6UJMtkRTHmbNW1VU_WQ">Đinh Phục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%E1%BA%A3i-T%C3%ADnh-Phu/Tr%E1%BB%AB-t%E1%BB%8Bch-c%E1%BA%A3m-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-9s35GWkDuY_kYKwdBOXuvQ">Trừ tịch cảm hứng - 除夕感興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%E1%BA%A3i-T%C3%ADnh-Phu/author-5VBdkDLCcLTpFT7k3ZzmYg">Ngải Tính Phu</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
